<dl><dd><i>Life and Times of Frederick Douglass</i>, first edition (1881)</dd>
<dd><i>Life and Times of Frederick Douglass</i>, reprinted (1882) <span class="scanlink" style="font-size: 83%;">(<a href="/wiki/Index:Life_and_Times_of_Frederick_Douglass_(1882).djvu" title="Index:Life and Times of Frederick Douglass (1882).djvu">transcription&#160;project</a>)</span></dd>
