<p>Some or all works by this author were published before January 1, 1931, and are in the <b><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Public_domain" class="extiw" title="w:Public domain">public domain</a></b> worldwide because the author died at least 100 years ago. Translations or editions published later may be copyrighted. Posthumous works may be <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_countries%27_copyright_length_based_on_publication_and_creation_dates" class="extiw" title="w:List of countries&#39; copyright length based on publication and creation dates">copyrighted based on how long they have been published</a> in certain countries and areas.
</p>
</div></div><div>
<p><span class="noimageRight"></span>
</p>
</div></div></div></div><div class="licensetpl">
<p><span class="licensetpl&#95;short">Public domain</span><span class="licensetpl&#95;long">Public domain</span><span class="licensetpl&#95;link&#95;req">false</span><span class="licensetpl&#95;attr&#95;req">false</span>
</p>
